WEBVTT

00:02:27.800 --> 00:02:30.096
Cunziderendi totu,
in America is crematzionis

00:02:30.120 --> 00:02:34.416
bogant donnia annu 300 milionis 
de tonnelladas de anidride carbonica

00:02:34.440 --> 00:02:36.120
in s'atmosfera.

00:02:38.080 --> 00:02:40.416
Sa beridadi

00:02:40.440 --> 00:02:44.320
est chi s'urtima cosa chi fadeus
in custa terra

00:02:45.040 --> 00:02:46.240
est a dda farenai.

00:02:51.120 --> 00:02:56.816
Eus creau, acetau e negau
sa morti fintzas a ponni

00:02:56.840 --> 00:03:00.456
cantu prus distantzia
fuet umanamenti possibili